originalSql:
SELECT 
    t.title AS movie_title,
    a.name AS actor_name,
    c.role_id AS role_id,
    m.name AS company_name,
    k.keyword AS movie_keyword
FROM 
    title t
JOIN 
    complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
JOIN 
    cast_info c ON cc.subject_id = c.person_id
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON c.person_id = a.person_id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name m ON mc.company_id = m.id
JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year > 2000
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year, a.name

INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "title"."id" = "s1"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "s1"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" > 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year", "aka_name"."name"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "keyword", "phonetic_code"
FROM "keyword"

SELECT COALESCE("title"."title", "title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_name"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "cast_info"."role_id" AS "ROLE_ID", "company_name"."name" AS "COMPANY_NAME", "s1"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "title"."production_year"
FROM "title"
INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "s1"."id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" > 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year", "aka_name"."name"
